videos.description: Kentucky's Tyrese Maxey picks Reggie Perry's pocket and takes it the other way for the double-clutch jam in transition.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Maxey steals and slams for UK's first points) 2020/02/04

videos.headline: Maxey steals and slams for UK's first points

videos.description: Kentucky's EJ Montgomery gets fouled while in the air and contorts to flip the ball in for the nifty and-1 finish.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Montgomery adjusts midair for acrobatic and-1) 2020/02/04

videos.headline: Montgomery adjusts midair for acrobatic and-1

videos.description: Immanuel Quickley drives to the hoop, draws an extra defender and tosses a lob to Nick Richards for the alley-oop slam.
videos.headline: Richards flushes alley-oop for Kentucky
